{"id": 59598, "date": "2025-09-07T04:00:08", "date_gmt": "2025-09-07T11:00:08", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59598"}, "modified": "2026-05-24T14:46:14", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-24T21:46:14", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-7-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/07/kingdom-of-days-september-7-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 7"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the as yet unnamed E Street Band headline during freshman orientation at Dean College in Franklin, Massachusetts.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29323\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1973-0906-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-0906.jpg?fit=645%2C1000&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"645,1000\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1973-0906\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-0906.jpg?fit=645%2C1000&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29323 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-0906.jpg?resize=645%2C1000&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"645\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-0906.jpg?w=645&amp;ssl=1 645w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-0906.jpg?resize=194%2C300&amp;ssl=1 194w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 645px) 100vw, 645px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20968\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1973-0907a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?fit=2429%2C634&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2429,634\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598820716&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1973-0907a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?fit=758%2C198&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20968 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?resize=758%2C198&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?w=2429&amp;ssl=1 2429w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?resize=300%2C78&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?resize=1024%2C267&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?resize=768%2C200&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?resize=1536%2C401&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?resize=2048%2C535&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1973-0907a.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975: </strong>Live at the Ya Ya Lounge in New Orleans, it&#8217;s&#8230; Lee Dorsey and the E Street Band? Bruce is on his way to the next tour stop in Texas, but the E Street Band stays behind in New Orleans to play a gig at the club without him. The gig is a barter for Dorsey lending his vocals on Southside Johnny&#8217;s upcoming Steve Van Zandt-produced album.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4239\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-0907/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0907.jpg?fit=490%2C490&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"490,490\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-0907\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0907.jpg?fit=490%2C490&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4239 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0907.jpg?resize=490%2C490&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0907.jpg?w=490&amp;ssl=1 490w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0907.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0907.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0907.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>In honor of Buddy Holly&#8217;s birthday, Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Rave On&#8221; as an encore at his Born in the U.S.A. show in Hartford. They won&#8217;t ever play it again (at least to date).</p>\n<div id=\"v-tkC2vmHI-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/tkC2vmHI?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20969\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-09-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?fit=1597%2C1644&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1597,1644\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598821016&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-09-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?fit=758%2C780&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20969 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?resize=758%2C780&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"780\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?w=1597&amp;ssl=1 1597w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?resize=291%2C300&amp;ssl=1 291w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?resize=995%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 995w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?resize=768%2C791&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?resize=1492%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1492w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-07.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1988</strong>: At the annual MTV Video Music Awards, &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/06/15/roll-of-the-dice-tunnel-of-love/\">Tunnel of Love</a>&#8221; loses in all five of its nominated categories: Video of the Year (to INXS&#8217; &#8220;Need You Tonight/Mediate&#8221;); Best Male Video (to Prince&#8217;s &#8220;U Got the Look&#8221;); Best Art Direction (to Squeeze&#8217;s &#8220;Hourglass&#8221;); Best Editing (again to INXS); and Viewer&#8217;s Choice (INXS).</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/M4K7XZGeHTE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>Night Two at Fenway Park on the Rising Tour features the tour premiere of &#8220;Frankie,&#8221; a reprise opener of &#8220;Diddy Wah Diddy&#8221; and a Peter Wolf guest appearance on the show-closing &#8220;Dirty Water.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-pgo0OErR-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/pgo0OErR?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KOQYe1Dbi8k?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20970\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-09-07a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?fit=2431%2C1644&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2431,1644\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598821585&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-09-07a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?fit=758%2C512&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20970 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?resize=758%2C513&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?w=2431&amp;ssl=1 2431w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?resize=300%2C203&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?resize=1024%2C692&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?resize=768%2C519&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?resize=1536%2C1039&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?resize=2048%2C1385&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-07a.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays his first-ever show at Wrigley Field in Chicago when the Wrecking Ball Tour arrives for the first of two nights, and what a show it is: Bruce opens with &#8220;Prove It All Night&#8221; with the Darkness Tour intro and tour premieres &#8220;None But the Brave.&#8221; Tom Morello and Eddie Vedder both make multiple guest appearances.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Pshj7jaGkck?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OuvujTkRiDE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LVgK3DNGIHc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20972\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2012-09-07a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07a.jpg?fit=1166%2C1648&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1166,1648\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598821838&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2012-09-07a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07a.jpg?fit=725%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20972 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07a.jpg?resize=758%2C1071&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1071\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07a.jpg?w=1166&amp;ssl=1 1166w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07a.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07a.jpg?resize=725%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 725w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07a.jpg?resize=768%2C1085&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07a.jpg?resize=1087%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1087w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20973\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2012-09-07b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07b.jpg?fit=1036%2C1643&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1036,1643\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598821887&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2012-09-07b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07b.jpg?fit=646%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20973 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07b.jpg?resize=758%2C1202&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1202\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07b.jpg?w=1036&amp;ssl=1 1036w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07b.jpg?resize=189%2C300&amp;ssl=1 189w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07b.jpg?resize=646%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 646w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07b.jpg?resize=768%2C1218&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2012-09-07b.jpg?resize=969%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 969w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>A show for the ages at Citizens Bank Park in Philadelphia&#8211;clocking in at 4:04, it remains Bruce&#8217;s longest show in the U.S. and his second longest show ever. The setlist continues the chronological &#8220;autobiography&#8221; theme of the victory lap, opening once again with a string-accompanied &#8220;New York City Serenade&#8221; and a stunning <em>eleven</em> pre-1974 songs. Philly specials abound: &#8220;The Fever&#8221; &#8220;Thundercrack,&#8221; and &#8220;Streets of Philadelphia&#8221; all make their tour debut.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HdiC-K2O06Y?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-