36&amp;ssl=1 931w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20975\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2016-09-07b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2016-09-07b.jpg?fit=632%2C1648&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"632,1648\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598822145&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2016-09-07b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2016-09-07b.jpg?fit=393%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20975 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2016-09-07b.jpg?resize=632%2C1648&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"632\" height=\"1648\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2016-09-07b.jpg?w=632&amp;ssl=1 632w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2016-09-07b.jpg?resize=115%2C300&amp;ssl=1 115w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2016-09-07b.jpg?resize=393%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 393w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2016-09-07b.jpg?resize=589%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 589w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 632px) 100vw, 632px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City. Following this show, Bruce takes a three-week break. Earlier in the day, Bruce and Patti attend Ralph Lauren&#8217;s 50th anniversary party at New York Fashion Week.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"12610\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2018-09-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2018-09-07.jpg?fit=400%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"400,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2018-09-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2018-09-07.jpg?fit=400%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12610 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2018-09-07.jpg?resize=400%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2018-09-07.jpg?w=400&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2018-09-07.jpg?resize=240%2C300&amp;ssl=1 240w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2021: </strong>On the 20th anniversary of the September 11th terror attacks, a new documentary film is released featuring Bruce&#8217;s narration. (Skip to the five-minute mark to hear Bruce&#8217;s contribution.)</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/atrdaj1mmLU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2023:\u00a0</strong>Bruce postpones his scheduled show in Syracuse to the following April due to his peptic ulcer disease.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"69433\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/07/kingdom-of-days-september-7-2/screenshot-2026-05-24-144542/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2026-05-24-144542.jpg?fit=966%2C972&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"966,972\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot 2026-05-24 144542\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2026-05-24-144542.jpg?fit=758%2C763&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-69433\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2026-05-24-144542.jpg?resize=758%2C763&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"763\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2026-05-24-144542.jpg?w=966&amp;ssl=1 966w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2026-05-24-144542.jpg?resize=298%2C300&amp;ssl=1 298w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2026-05-24-144542.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2026-05-24-144542.jpg?resize=768%2C773&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2026-05-24-144542.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2024:\u00a0</strong>After more than a year and two postponements, Bruce and the E Street Band take the stage in Nationals Park In Washington, D.C.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/yR5ELD4LcPA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDyR5ELD4LcPA\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nZnkmNiQZs0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDnZnkmNiQZs0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce plays Wrigley Field for the first time, and in Philadelphia he sets the unbroken record for his longest American show. Plus: the E Street Band plays a gi